HEADWORD: Airwoman
<hw>Air"wom`an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A woman who ascends
or flies in an aircraft; a woman aviator; a woman airplane pilot or
balloonist; an aviatrix.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> aviatrix, aviatress</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

